title: 藏器于身 || Hidden Surprise
description:
从这里开始会有很多好康的
之前我常用的aom模型已经看腻了，而且aom的一些特性跟我以后的方向有冲突，所以我的主模型换到了cetusmix，之后的作品大概都会更偏向扁平化
另外c站上的模型已经不太能满足我的创作想法，我已经开始尝试自己炼lora，这一期就是用我自己的lora创作，效果很好

I'm switching to cetusmix from aom3 beacause I'm tired of its style and it has some traits that conflict with my ideas. So my works' style after this will be more flat than before.
Lora models from civitai are not enough for my ideas now, so I'm trying to train my own Lora, this one is using one of them. Works quite well for me.
